<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177990>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Baeoneurela benefica (female, SEM): (a) head, frontoventral, emphasising the clypaeus, antennal rim and interantennal process; (b) head, dorsofrontal; (c) back of the head, emphasising the preoccipital furrow; (d) mandible; (e) mesosoma, dorsal; (f) mesosoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177994>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Baeoneurella phaeax (female,SEM):(a) head, ventral view; (b) head, frontal view; (c) head,lateral view; (d) head, posterodorsal view; (e) back of the head; (f) mesosoma, dorsal; (g) mesosoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177994/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177998>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Baeoneurella mirabilis (female, SEM): (a) head, frontoventral; (b) head, frontodorsal; (c) head, posterodorsal; (d) back of head; (e) mesosoma, dorsal; (f) mesosoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177998/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178002>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Baeoneurella maceki (female, SEM): (a) head, ventrolaterally; (b) head, frontal view; (c) head, dorsal; (d) back of the head; (e) mesosoma, dorsal; (f) mesosoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178002/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178006>
    dc:description "Figure 13. (a) Baeoneurella bicolor; (b) Baeoneurella blissae; (c) Baeoneurella cumaea (a–c: habitus; a1–c1: head and mesosoma, detail)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178006/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5178008>
    dc:description "Figure 14. (a) Baeoneurella cf. nigra; (b) Baeoneurella platythoracis; (c) Telenomus OP1701 (a–c: habitus; a1–c1: head and mesosoma, detail)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5178008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177986>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Back of the head in (a) Iphitrachelus sp; (b) Acerotella sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

